First Department,

March, 1981

(March 3, 1981) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Robert Gorman, Appellant.

Judgment, Supreme Court, New York County, rendered on January 16, 1980, unanimously affirmed. The case is remitted to the Supreme Court, New York County, for further proceedings pursuant to CPL 460.50 (subd 5). No opinion. Concur — Murphy, P. J., Sandler, Carro, Lupiano and Fein, JJ.
